 Java Event Scheduler Project
Overview
This project is a console-based Event Scheduler that allows users to:

Add events with specific dates and times.

View all scheduled events.

Check for upcoming events.

Calculate the duration until an event.

List events within a specific date range.

The application leverages Java 8's java.time package, ensuring thread safety and immutability.


